OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FThe 2025-26 football campaign has
OL,7,Ffinished with mixed fortunes for clubs
OL,8,Facross our region.
OL,10,FThere was glory for the likes of AFC
OL,11,FBournemouth and Brighton & Hove
OL,12,FAlbion, who both secured European
OL,13,Ffootball for next season.
OL,15,FFans of Oxford United, meanwhile, will
OL,16,Falready be willing the start of league
OL,17,Ffootball again in August, after
OL,18,Fsuffering relegation from the
OL,19,FChampionship.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
