OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779894668
OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FHere's a full rundown of how all of
OL,7,Four clubs from League Two to the
OL,8,FPremier League got on this season.
OL,10,FAFC Bournemouth
OL,12,FThe Cherries enjoyed their best ever
OL,13,Fleague campaign, finishing sixth in
OL,14,Fthe Premier League and qualifying for
OL,15,FEurope for the first time in the
OL,16,Fclub's history.
OL,18,FTheir haul of 57 points was enough to
OL,19,Fclaim a spot in next season's UEFA
OL,20,FEuropa League, with supporters already
OL,21,Fdreaming of trips across the continent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
