OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779894668
OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FIt was a fitting send off for outgoing
OL,7,Fhead coach Andoni Iraola, who leaves
OL,8,Fthe Dorset-based outfit this summer
OL,9,Fafter three years in charge.
OL,11,FBrighton & Hove Albion
OL,13,FBrighton also guaranteed European
OL,14,Ffootball for next season, despite
OL,15,Fslipping to a 3-0 home defeat against
OL,16,FManchester United on the final day of
OL,17,Fthe league campaign.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
