OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FThe only previous time that the
OL,7,FSeagulls have played in Europe came
OL,8,Fduring the 2023-24 season, when they
OL,9,Fparticipated in the Europa League.
OL,11,FBut they will still make club history
OL,12,Fnext season when they begin competing
OL,13,Fin the UEFA Conference League for the
OL,14,Ffirst time.
OL,16,FSouthampton
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
