OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FA rollercoaster season for Southampton
OL,7,Fsaw the club go from fighting
OL,8,Frelegation to playing an FA Cup semi-
OL,9,Ffinal at Wembley and securing a
OL,10,Fplayoff finish.
OL,12,FHowever, all that good work was undone
OL,13,Fwhen allegations of spying emerged,
OL,14,Fwith the Saints ultimately found
OL,15,Fguilty and expelled from the playoffs.
OL,17,FIt's left many Saints fans wondering
OL,18,Fwhat the future holds for a number of
OL,19,Fkey figures at the club, including
OL,20,Fincumbent head coach Tonda Eckert.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
