OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FA strong end of season run-in helped
OL,7,Fensure that Portsmouth will remain a
OL,8,FChampionship club for next season.
OL,10,FJohn Mousinho's side lost just one of
OL,11,Ftheir final eight league fixtures,
OL,12,Fwith that defeat coming against
OL,13,Feventual champions Coventry City.
OL,15,FPompey's survival means there will be
OL,16,Fat least another year of league
OL,17,Fmeetings with fierce south coast
OL,18,Frivals Southampton.
OL,20,FOxford United
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
