OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779894668
OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FThere was less good news for fans of
OL,7,FOxford United as their side dropped
OL,8,Fout of the Championship into League
OL,9,FOne.
OL,11,FOxford finished four points from
OL,12,Fsafety in the end, with a run of only
OL,13,Ftwo wins in their last nine matches
OL,14,Fcondemning the U's to their fate.
OL,16,FReading's hopes of finishing this
OL,17,Fseason in the play off places were
OL,18,Fdashed by a poor spell of form, which
OL,19,Fsaw the Royals win just two of their
OL,20,Flast 11 league games.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
