OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FLeam Richardson will be hoping his
OL,7,Fside can go one better next season in
OL,8,Fa division which will contain former
OL,9,FPremier League champions Leicester
OL,10,FCity.
OL,12,FGillingham ended the season neither
OL,13,Fchallenging for promotion or in danger
OL,14,Fof being relegated, claiming a 17th
OL,15,Fplaced finish in League Two.
OL,17,FThe Gills will hope gaffer Gareth
OL,18,FAinsworth's history of winning
OL,19,Fpromotion with Wycombe Wanderers can
OL,20,Fbe translated into their own on-field
OL,21,Fsuccess next season.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
