OL,3,CHow did the 2025-26 season go for our
OL,4,Cfootball clubs?
OL,6,FCrawley Town
OL,8,FCrawley narrowly avoided dropping out
OL,9,Fof the English Football League,
OL,10,Ffinishing just one point ahead of 23rd
OL,11,Fplaced Harrogate Town.
OL,13,FIt looks set to be a big summer for
OL,14,Fhead coach Colin Kazim-Richards, who
OL,15,Fwill be expecting to deliver a marked
OL,16,Fimprovement in results next season.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
